- we can plan and conduct this whole tenure at its utmost potential

Happy 21st birthday AMSA-Indonesia!
At first, what I know about AMSA is that it is one of FKUI's many organizations. My very first project in AMSA is PRICE EAMSC in which I was appointed as the Project Officer of that event. In that event, I tried my best to fulfill my duty. It turned out that, it was so much fun. It was a big success and by that event I got to know a lot of AMSA members from other universities. Through a few events in AMSA, I realized that this is what I want to do this for the rest of my uni life. Then, with lots of supports from my friends in AMSA, I decided to apply for AMSA-Elite Chairperson. And this, was the choice that I would never regret in my whole life. 
Being a part of AMSA taught me how to survive university life through having lots of friends all around Indonesia and even wider. I experienced lots of fun through making friends, deepening my knowledge, and spreading positive impacts through social acts to the surroundings. I experienced my best moment in AMSA in every moment that I had in AMSA.

caption.text:
Taukah kamu?

Saat ini, penyakit jantung merupakan penyebab kematian no.2 di Indonesia. Kematian akibat henti jantung dapat terjadi dalam 10 menit dan tatalaksana awal yang disebut Bantuan Hidup Dasar merupakan satu satunya kesempatan korban untuk bertahan hidup. Namun, seringkali bantuan ambulans datang terlambat sehingga nyawa korban tidak dapat diselamatkan.
Staying Alive adalah sebuah organisasi independen yang bertujuan menurunkan angka kematian akibat henti jantung di Indonesia dengan fokus utama menyediakan media pelaporan kejadian henti jantung dan memberikan pelatihan BHD. 
Dengan menjadi follower akun line official Staying Alive di @stayingalive (line@), anda bisa melaporkan kejadian henti jantung di sekitar anda sehingga penolong terdekat dapat memberikan BHD sembari menunggu ambulans.

Ayo selamatkan nyawa dan jadi pahlawan!
